Package uk.ac.manchester.spinnaker.machine

Class ChipLocation

java.lang.Object
uk.ac.manchester.spinnaker.machine.ChipLocation
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<ChipLocation>, HasChipLocation
public final class ChipLocation
extends Object
implements HasChipLocation, Comparable<ChipLocation>
The location of a Chip as an X and Y tuple.

This class is final as it is used a key in maps.

Author:
alan, dkf

  • Field Summary

    Fields 
    Modifier and Type Field Description
    static ChipLocation ONE_ZERO
    The location (1,0), which is the one to the east/right of the bottom/left corner.
    static ChipLocation ZERO_ZERO
    The location (0,0), which is in the bottom/left corner and typically the ethernet chip for the lead board of an allocation.
